## Privacy Policy {#privacy}

**Last updated: [Date you submit]**

Dino & Animal Trivia ("the App") is a locally-stored, device-only application. The App does not collect, transmit, store, sell, or share any personal data with any party.

### What We Store Locally

The App uses your device's local storage to save:
- Your player profiles and customization choices (names, badges, titles, themes, sound packs, win animations)
- Your game progress, statistics, and earned achievements
- Your DinoCoin balance and purchased cosmetic items
- Your in-app preferences (active theme, sound toggles, etc.)

This data is stored on your device only. It is not transmitted to any server, and the developer has no access to it.

### No Third-Party Services

The App does not use any third-party analytics, advertising, tracking, or crash-reporting services.

### No Purchases

The App contains no in-app purchases and no real-money transactions. DinoCoins are an in-game currency earned entirely by playing the App — they have no real-world value.

### Children

The App is suitable for all ages. Because the App does not collect any personal data, it complies with COPPA (the US Children's Online Privacy Protection Act) and similar laws by not collecting anything from users of any age in the first place.

### Data Deletion

All App data is stored on your device. To remove everything, either:
- Use the Reset options in Settings inside the App, or
- Delete the App from your device (iOS will remove all associated data)

